%h1 Register and Log In
%h4 Welcome Bridge Designer! We're open for individuals who want to test their skill and for unofficial local contests.

%p
  If you've already registered, then log in by typing your Team Name and Password below.

.row
  .span6.offset3
    = form_for(:session, :url => session_path) do |f|

      = f.label 'Team Name:'
      = f.text_field :name 

      = f.label 'Team Password:'
      = f.password_field :password

      = f.submit 'Log In'

%hr
.row
  .span6.offset3
    If you have not yet registered, then...
    = button_to 'Start the Registration Wizard >>', new_team_path, :method => :get
